% SOURCE: [HH21], ┬¦3.1, type of a T-fixed Higgs bundle
%   (read from references/MR4411733-stable-higgs-bundles.tex)
% SOURCE QUOTE: We call the ordered partition $(\rank(L_0),...,\rank(L_k))$ of $n$ the {\em
